casebody.data:
No. —, original.

Ex parte: In the matter of Joseph Y. Saunders. May 16, 1927. Mr. Joseph Y. Saunders, pro se.

-The motion for leave to file petition for writ-of habeas corpus is denied without prejudice to the filing of a petition for writ of habeas corpus in the District Court of the United States for the District of Georgia.
